Name: MOMO.EXE
About the game: Momo is a nickname given to a sculpture of a young woman with long black hair, large bulging eyes, a wide smile and bird legs. Pictures of the sculpture are associated with an urban legend involving a WhatsApp phone number that messages disturbing photographs to those that attempt to contact it, linked to a game referred to as the 'Momo Challenge' or 'Momo Game.' You got bored and you decided to type a message... KEY FEATURES: ◆ Interactive story with a lot of choices tasks to complete ◆ Very scary horror - MOMO will come for YOU ◆ Fully intractable phone like in real life ◆ Flashlight... in the phone ◆ Achievements
